File structure for portimg:

/           - portimg's root
/admin      - All of portimg's admin functionality goes here.
/classes    - Contains the php files that hold object classes.
/css        - Holds all of the site level style sheets used in the site
/images     - Site level images are here ( portimg logo... )
/lib        - any helper files go here
/main       - Homepage for the site is located here
/mike       - An example user
    /gallery1   - A gallery belonging to mike.




